data.description: Price Improvement Alert! Welcome to your future home in Miami! This immaculate 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom townhome is nestled near the vibrant Miami Zoo, offering a perfect blend of convenience and tranquility. Meticulously maintained, this residence boasts a modern and updated kitchen and remodeled bathroom, ensuring both style and functionality. The spacious floor plan creates an inviting atmosphere throughout, with a generously sized master bedroom providing a peaceful retreat. New LG washer and dryer. Ideal for those looking to make their first home purchase, this townhome offers comfort and charm in every corner. Step outside to discover your own private backyard, perfect for grilling and entertaining guests. Enjoy the Florida sunshine in the privacy of your outdoor space.
